' pixaGetFont(dir, fontsize, pbl0, pbl1, pbl2) as Pixa
' pixaGetFont(const char *, l_int32, l_int32 *, l_int32 *, l_int32 *) as PIXA *
'''  <summary>
''' <para/>
''' Notes:<para/>
''' (1) This reads a pre-computed pixa file with the 95 ascii chars.<para/>
